The paper discusses graph pattern matching, which is a common problem in databases (cs.DB) and graph algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses hardware acceleration, which falls under computer architecture (cs.AR). The paper's focus on concurrency and memory locality suggests it may also fall under systems and networking (cs.SI). Finally, the use of relational join algorithms suggests it may also fall under programming languages (cs.PL).
